description:
Good morning and welcome the ride!  Ask Mr. Ready to Love contains pregnancy triangulation, to tell or not to tell?  Are people tired of Yeezus?  A man has cut off his wife's driving privileges of his car.  Deion Sanders is back in headlines and they are talking about him.  What is going on Dallas!?!?  In Junior's Sports Report, Tommy's comment about Tom Brady was savage AF.  Would You Rather covered your wife.  Today the show ends with Tommy's story and best for last Happy Birthday Mrs. H!!!
